==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Wanghee
<hw>Wang*hee"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Chin.
<ets>wang</ets> yellow + <ets>he<?/</ets> a root.]</ety>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>The Chinese name of one or two species of bamboo,
or jointed cane, of the genus <gen>Phyllostachys</gen>. The slender
stems are much used for walking sticks.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>whanghee</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

